ssets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個template整合好唔少國際組織嘅email (包括外國Head office)，唔該和理非唔好淨係去信香港office，同我炸爆外國office嘅email！因為我地唔單止要佢哋香港office出聲，更重要係要佢哋發揮佢哋喺國際社會嘅影響力，話畀全世界聽香港情況幾恐怖，要求國際社會增援！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSince June 2019, Hong Kong has been facing a serious humanitarian crisis. While Hongkongers continue to suffer from grave violations of fundamental rights, as influential civil society actors with long histories of championing for human rights, child rights, and environmental justice, IGOs and INGOs have failed to fulfill their primary mission in protecting Hongkongers by remaining in silence.<br />\nThis is not a time to appease to specific political powers, but rather a time that requires immediate aid regardless of political stance. For this reason, my friends and I have created this letter template that can be sent to various IGOs and INGOs.<br />\n<br />\nPlease join us in sending out this email to call for their immediate action to fulfill their primary responsibilities and protect the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1kqARKNNydQg267pX788vNJ5XwCJmOrdZ1l9iLJBHqps/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1kqARKNNydQg267pX788vNJ5XwCJmOrdZ1l9iLJBHqps%2Fedit&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=9a6658b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1kqARKNNydQg267pX788vNJ5XwCJmOrdZ1l9iLJBHqps/edit</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n麻煩晒各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b45e278342000b39e71c55dca2cb668293aed2","tid":1741690,"uid":237956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}